description: Located just off the Heights and steps to the beach, this beautifully maintained single-family home is filled with natural light from its southern-facing windows on every level. The finished lower level offers a spacious family room with a full home theater system- perfect for entertaining and allowing you to easily add an additional bedroom! Enjoy a newly renovated eat-in kitchen with quartz countertops, cherry cabinets, and stainless steel appliances on the main living level.  Upstairs, you’ll find two oversized bedrooms with custom closets and a full bath. The crown jewel? A massive private roof deck with sweeping views of Dorchester Bay and the Harbor Islands—ideal for relaxing or hosting. Complete with deeded driveway parking, a high-efficiency Navien combi boiler and split system, ample storage throughout, and a washer and dryer. You won’t want to miss this location by South Boston’s best parks and beaches, public transportation, highway access, and vibrant retail options.
